name: London views - 02 - Kentish Town on 06/05/2021
description: Music part “2021 05” produced in May 2021 at GBL Studios in London, UK. Video filmed on May 6th 2021 in the PM outside Kentish Town tube station, still in London, UK. Execution and editing by Matteo Manzini @matteomanzini__ (Twitter/Instagram). “Not sure where I’m heading with this project, especially for images, but I’ve always wanted to document ordinary days in my city”.
